  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Exclusive Multifunction Survival Device",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属多功能生存装置",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊多功能求生裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>. This weapon comes with the tactical <span class=\"name name-technology\">Paralysis Mortar</span> and lethal <span class=\"name name-technology\">Blaze Javelin</span> pre-installed, for disabling aggressors and delivering powerful shots.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。这款武器预装了战术性的<span class=\"name name-technology\">瘫痪迫击炮</span>和致命的<span class=\"name name-technology\">火焰标枪</span>，可以支持强有力的射击并使敌人丧失行动能力。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收下</span>这个多用途工具，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的多用途工具<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分切换可用的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。這把步槍預裝了戰術性的<span class=\"name name-technology\">癱瘓迫擊砲</span>與致命的<span class=\"name name-technology\">火焰標槍</span>，能夠癱瘓攻擊者並發射強大的射擊。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>皆可。在星球上時，可利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 中的機能選項切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
